(332, 'Emory Healthcare', 'healthcare', 'The Environment Agency is an Executive NDPB responsible to the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs. Its principal aims are to protect and improve the environment and to promote sustainable development. It plays a central role in delivering the environmental priorities of Central Government including Flood and Coastal Erosion Risk Management, Climate Change Adaptation and Mitigation, Water Quality and Waste Management.', 'https://www.google.co.in/search?q=dsv&oq=dsv&aqs=chrome..69i57j0l5.1403j0j7&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8/fragflag', 'hacked', '-12,844,498', 'Spyware', 1),
