(861, 'Educational Credit Management Corporation', 'financial', 'The ESRC funds research into the big social and economic questions facing society today.  ESRC also develops and trains the UK''s future social scientists.  ESRC''s research informs public policies and helps make businesses, voluntary bodies and other organisations more effective.', 'https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox/iosid/portid', 'hacked', '-10,653,410', 'Ransomware', 1),
